<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:198'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='198:214'>　周易章句證異　　　　　易類</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='214:220'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='220:242'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案周易章句證異十二卷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='242:265'>　　　國朝翟均亷撰均亷字春沚仁和人官内閣中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='265:288'>　　　　書是編取周易上下經古今本同異之處互</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='288:311'>　　　　相考證如李鼎祚卦辭前分冠序卦周燔卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='311:335'>　　　　辭前列大象卦辭復列彖𫝊趙汝楳卦辭前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='335:361'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='361:384'>　　　　列大象卦辭後列彖傳次文言次爻辭李過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='384:407'>　　　　方逢辰乾卦卦辭後列彖傳次文言釋彖處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='407:430'>　　　　次大象次爻辭蔡淵卦辭後列大象次彖傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='430:453'>　　　　文言别為一傳傳低一字王洙于經中不載</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='453:476'>　　　　卦辭别為一篇之類此篇章之同異也如乾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='476:499'>　　　　卦三爻孟喜作夕惕若夤句厲无咎句苟爽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='499:522'>　　　　虞翻王弼作夕惕若厲句邵子朱震朱子作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='522:545'>　　　　夕惕若句此句讀之同異也遂卦逐爻悉為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='545:571'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='571:594'>　　　　臚列間或附以己意以亷案二字别之古今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='594:617'>　　　　本異同之處校勘頗為精宻雖近時之書而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='617:640'>　　　　所言皆有依據轉勝郭京舉正以意刋改託</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='640:663'>　　　　言于王韓舊本者也乾隆四十五年十一月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='663:672'>　　　　恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='672:704'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='704:730'>　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸　費　墀</span><br/>
</p>
